To evaluate how forecast skill decreases with increasing lead times, we analyzed the performance of the selected models across horizons from 30 to 360 minutes. As shown in Table 1, the predictive accuracy exhibits a characteristic decay as the forecast horizon extends5. The highest precision is achieved at the 30-minute lag (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
